          ],
          "heading": "Leave and Flexibility / Onboarding Support / Claims Support",
          "structure_kind": "text",
          "start_offset": 0,
          "end_offset": 310,
          "excerpt": "Full-time employees receive 12 days of annual leave in the first year.\nThe hybrid work arrangement allows up to two remote days per week.\n\nNew hires receive a mentor for the first 30 days.\n新進同仁需在到職後七天內完成資訊安全課程。\n\n福利手冊只說明公司提供醫療與心理健康資源，沒有列出正式理賠審核天數。",
